{"tid":2327713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女大專生涉阻差辦公 辯方質疑警認錯人 莫子聰裁定罪名成立 還押候判","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T14:01:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bca230e951b0ca5dabc5549c87132a89491430ae","tid":2327713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12184&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=ea568dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12184</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第八庭 #續審<br />\n#莫子聰裁判官 #審訊 [2/1]<br />\n👤劉(20) #1114將軍澳 #阻差辦公 <br />\n<br />\n控罪: 阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員 <br />\n被控於2019年11月14日在將軍澳唐俊街將軍澳港鐵站A出口外，故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警員21417張德俊。 <br />\n<br />\n🛑罪名成立🛑<br />\n<br />\n還押2021年 1月6日 14:30判刑。因莫子聰裁判官認為被告審訊後被定罪沒有悔意，除非社會服務今報告證明被告有強烈悔意，否則即時監禁無可避免。<br />\n<br />\n裁決理由19:00左右upload"},{"pid":"684d7c42925c9cf3753757f4325bcd83d24c2792","tid":2327713,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"辯方庭上播出片段，稱涉案過程只約3至4秒，質疑警員供稱被告阻礙的時間不合理，警員作供稱5至6秒只是他的「現場感覺」，並指出片段模糊，或未能看清整個事發過程。<br />\n<br />\n警員張德俊供稱，當晚約10時接報到將軍澳港鐵站一帶掃蕩。他與3名同袍乘警車到場後，因警車受地上磚頭及雜物阻礙而下車，他望向港鐵站時，看到一名金髮女子與其他黑衣人逃跑，他隨即追截。<br />\n<br />\n張德俊承認追截期間，金髮女曾消失在視線內約5秒。張德俊再望到她時，便上前用警棍打了她的右大腿一下，令她失平衡向前傾。張德俊本打算順勢將金髮女制服在地，但被告突然在前方出現，雙手扯着她的右手臂約5至6秒欲拉走她，令張德俊制服失敗。警員楊晉熙不久後趕到制服被告後，張德俊才成功制服金髮女。張表示，被告的出現令他浪費更多時間才能制服金髮女。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時，質疑張德俊調亂被告與金髮女的身分，並表示當日被告並非突然出現，而是與金髮女手拖手逃跑。張德俊承認從無詢問被告及金髮女的身分，但強調自己曾簡單查問金髮女子，亦認得兩人外表，故否認有調亂。"},{"pid":"eefb927aa25ce34ada9c4c6b5b72d1c5fcd3b55d","tid":2327713,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86fec4d0af49b73d561346276a1ab37295a403b2","tid":2327713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eefb927aa25ce34ada9c4c6b5b72d1c5fcd3b55d","tid":2327713,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033072ee01faeca9b3f673b756380f597839d131","tid":2327713,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba8e56065342f8cbd0934e48afe63e12578185d8","tid":2327713,"uid":218544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26ee5300e7b914450e9713d7bd155185c48f6587","tid":2327713,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dbb3310503828f0353dcbb17f7bd17d87adea0","tid":2327713,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07d88ee081c2e513a42431d01ad199d8d3edd19","tid":2327713,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"968c578ec0fc7fe02a331150860db48d599b8908","tid":2327713,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bb854052c52c0709fd10de1213e3f23f9591b9","tid":2327713,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse